name: CONTEGO - KIPLING
description: www.ihlet.com The Contego KIPLING SUNGLASSES have been hand picked by the IHLET "Exclusives" team and meet the highest standards in quality materials and craftsmanship. Brooklyn, NY based eyewear brand CONTEGO delivers quality products with distinct style. Handcrafted acetate frames with stainless steel hardware backed by a strong manufactures warranty. As if that was'nt enough, every frame sold CONTEGO and RestoringVision.org will donate a pair of prescription glasses to those less fortunate. Handcrafted Navy Matte Acetate Frame. 1. Red CR39 Lens is UV Ray protectant, significantly reduce the glare from reflective surfaces & have a high abrasion resistance. 2. Both temples are embellished with a stainless steel Contego™ umbrella logo and two Contego™ drops on the front of each frame. 3. Both temples are fitted with stainless steel optical spring hinges.
